{"tid":1480901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民運動日","createTime":"2019-08-17T13:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:49:23.000Z","uid":170291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d3667df5122c998f459fc11c7cc4d9bd3aed11ec","tid":1480901,"uid":170291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:23:50.000Z","msg":"香港人最近都好鍾意做運動 今日想介紹下美式足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然比較冷門 但絕對學到好多技巧 前提係要1on1 比人圍嘅話就比較難用 始終三十六計走為上計<br />\n<br />\n1. Tackle <br />\n一個好嘅tackle絕對係運動場上有幫助 記得落地要保護自己<br />\n8:05<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kLldjE6vvFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkLldjE6vvFs&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=bb22bf9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kLldjE6vvFs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. Stiff arm<br />\n假設有人差唔多要tackle你 你可以用隻手㩒住佢推開佢 記得要lower body<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UuyAjmVFvtE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUuyAjmVFvtE&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=979fad58\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UuyAjmVFvtE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4xKUOgGZCdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4xKUOgGZCdk&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=f0751a21\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4xKUOgGZCdk</a>即使唔夠啲裝備勁嘅人大力 但起碼可以平衡到自己冇咁容易比佢地捉住<br />\n<br />\n3. Truck<br />\n同樣情況 如果身型有翻咁上下 通常對手tackle之前都會伸隻手出黎 你可以睇準時機打落去或者揮上去<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ctFK6ApBRV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FctFK6ApBRV4&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=d2de9be5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ctFK6ApBRV4</a><br />\n運動細胞好嘅你地可以練習下 對於其他人黎講就比較難用<br />\n<br />\n美式足球最重要嘅一點就係唔好比人捉到/tackle到 提多次以上嘅技巧只係保護自己或1on1嘅時候用 希望大家學以致用 打贏對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc2a73c9c0a945bed70729525c3bc26134dacca","tid":1480901,"uid":170291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}